# Stage 4: AST construction

Semantic resolution, folding and HIR-ready output.

## Contract

- Input: sorted headers, visibility maps, builtin declarations and external package metadata
- Output: typed AST nodes, `TypeEnvironment`, constants, template handoff data and reactive metadata
- Decides: declaration resolution, body semantics, type checking, terminality, template semantics
- Must not decide: HIR control-flow shape, borrow facts, backend lowering
- Invariant: generics, traits and cast evidence resolve before HIR

## Main paths

- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/mod.rs`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/module_ast/environment/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/module_ast/emission/`
- `src/compiler_frontend/ast/module_ast/finalization/`

